# This directory stores user voice samples for enrollment.
# Required files:
#   enrollment.wav - 30 seconds of the user speaking naturally
#   verification_1.wav - Short verification sample
#   verification_2.wav - Short verification sample
#   verification_3.wav - Short verification sample
#
# These are used for:
# 1. Speaker identification (who is speaking)
# 2. Voice activity threshold calibration
# 3. Wake word sensitivity tuning